5em !important;\">C</span><span class=\"cangc4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #227cbe; font-family: Impact; font-size: 0.9em !important;\">LEAN</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"cangc3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #227cbe; font-family: Impact; font-size: 1.15em !important;\">A</span><span class=\"cangc4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #227cbe; font-family: Impact; font-size: 0.9em !important;\">S</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"cangc3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #227cbe; font-family: Impact; font-size: 1.15em !important;\">N</span><span class=\"cangc4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #227cbe; font-family: Impact; font-size: 0.9em !important;\">EW</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; font-size: 0.65em; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: 0px !important; color: #227cbe; font-weight: 900;\">&reg;</span>&rsquo;s revolutionary cleaning approach for heat exchangers and many other parts in the refinery and petrochemical industries.</p>\r\n<p><iframe id=\"player\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Oswald, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\" title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rcM1fKiADXU?autoplay=1&amp;controls=1&amp;autohide=0&amp;rel=0&amp;enablejsapi=1&amp;origin=http%3A%2F%2Flocalhost%3A3000&amp;widgetid=1\" width=\"797\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"1\" data-gtm-yt-inspected-31555613_36=\"true\" data-gtm-yt-inspected-31555613_38=\"true\" data-gtm-yt-inspected-31555613_40=\"true\" data-gtm-yt-inspected-31555613_42=\"true\"></iframe></p>', 'en', NULL, '2020-12-24 05:46:45'),
(2, '22222222', '<h2><span style=\"color: #000000; background-color: #ffffff;\">Join Us &ndash; Events</span></h2>', '<h2>Join Us &ndash; Events</h2>\n            <ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n            <li><a href=\"https://l.feathr.co/landing-page---2020-aiche---exhibitor-clean-as-new\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">AIChE &ndash; Virtual Conference</a>&nbsp;&ndash; August 17-21, 2020</li>\n            <li><a href=\"https://www.afpm.org/events/27741b00000003\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">AFPM &ndash; Virtual Conference</a>&nbsp;&ndash; August 25-27, 2020</li>\n            <li><a href=\"https://www.heat-exchanger-world.com/hxw-americas-2020/introducing-heat-exchanger-world-conference-and-expo-americas\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" aria-invalid=\"true\">Heat Exchanger World Conference and Expo Americas</a>&nbsp;&ndash; November 18-19, 2020</li>\n            </ul>', 'en', NULL, NULL),
(3, '11111111', '<p>CLEAN ASNEW&reg;精选于ManufacturingMarvels&reg;</p>', '<p>最初在2020年9月1日的《福克斯商业新闻》上播出，《 ManufacturingMarvels&reg;》采用了CLEAN ASNEW&reg;的革命性清洁方法，用于热交换器以及炼油和石化行业的许多其他零件。</p>', 'cn', '2020-12-24 05:54:11', '2020-12-24 05:54:11'),
(4, '11111111', '<p>CLEAN AS NEW&reg; Destacado en Manufacturing Marvels&reg;</p>', '<p>Transmitido originalmente en Fox Business News el 1 de septiembre de 2020, Manufacturing Marvels&reg; presenta el revolucionario enfoque de limpieza CLEAN AS NEW&reg; para intercambiadores de calor y muchas otras partes en las industrias de refiner&iacute;a y petroqu&iacute;mica.</p>', 'es-us', '2020-12-24 05:55:14', '2020-12-24 05:55:14'),
(5, '22222222', '<p>&Uacute;nase a nosotros - Eventos</p>', '<p>AIChE - Conferencia virtual - 17-21 de agosto de 2020</p>\r\n<p>AFPM - Conferencia virtual - 25-27 de agosto de 2020</p>\r\n<p>Conferencia y Exposici&oacute;n Mundial de Intercambiadores de Calor de las Am&eacute;ricas - 18-19 de noviembre de 2020</p>', 'es-us', '2020-12-24 05:55:49', '2020-12-24 05:55:49');

