(20, '22222222', '22222222', 'Shell Deer Park', '<p>Je pensais que tout ce que vous faisiez était génial et j\'ai déjà diffusé des recommandations pour continuer à vous utiliser chaque fois que nous le pouvons!</p>', '/assets/img/feedback/Shell-Deer-Park.jpg', 'Gestionnaire de redressement', 'Feedback', 'fr', NULL, NULL),
(21, '22222222', '22222222', 'Shell Deer Park', '<p>मुझे लगा कि आप लोगों ने जो कुछ भी किया वह भयानक था और जब भी हम कर सकते हैं आप लोगों का उपयोग जारी रखने के लिए पहले से ही सिफारिशें फैला रहे हैं!</p>', '/assets/img/feedback/Shell-Deer-Park.jpg', 'टर्नअराउंड मैनेजर', 'Feedback', 'hi-in', NULL, NULL),
(22, '22222222', '22222222', 'Shell Deer Park', '<p>私はあなたたちがしたことはすべて素晴らしいと思いました、そして私たちができるときはいつでもあなたたちを使い続けるための推奨事項をすでに広めています！</p>', '/assets/img/feedback/Shell-Deer-Park.jpg', 'ターンアラウンドマネージャー', 'Feedback', 'jp', NULL, NULL),
(23, '22222222', '22222222', 'Shell Deer Park', '<p>Saya rasa semua yang anda lakukan adalah hebat dan telah menyebarkan cadangan untuk terus menggunakan anda setiap kali kami boleh!</p>', '/assets/img/feedback/Shell-Deer-Park.jpg', 'Pengurus Giliran', 'Feedback', 'ml', NULL, NULL),
(24, '22222222', '22222222', 'Shell Deer Park', '<p>¡Pensé que todo lo que hicieron fue increíble y ya he estado difundiendo recomendaciones para seguir usándolos siempre que podamos!</p>', '/assets/img/feedback/Shell-Deer-Park.jpg', 'Gerente de Turnaround', 'Feedback', 'mx', NULL, NULL),
(25, '22222222', '22222222', 'Shell Deer Park', '<p>ਮੈਂ ਸੋਚਿਆ ਕਿ ਤੁਹਾਡੇ ਦੁਆਰਾ ਕੀਤਾ ਸਭ ਕੁਝ ਸ਼ਾਨਦਾਰ ਸੀ ਅਤੇ ਪਹਿਲਾਂ ਹੀ ਸਿਫਾਰਸ਼ਾਂ ਫੈਲਾ ਰਿਹਾ ਹੈ ਕਿ ਤੁਸੀਂ ਮੁੰਡਿਆਂ ਨੂੰ ਵਰਤਣਾ ਜਾਰੀ ਰੱਖੋ ਜਦੋਂ ਵੀ ਅਸੀਂ ਕਰ ਸਕਦੇ ਹਾਂ!</p>', '/assets/img/feedback/Shell-Deer-Park.jpg', 'ਮੋੜ ਪ੍ਰਬੰਧਕ', 'Feedback', 'pa-pk', NULL, NULL),
(26, '22222222', '22222222', 'Shell Deer Park', '<p>Achei incrível tudo o que vocês fizeram e já estou espalhando recomendações para continuar usando vocês sempre que pudermos!</p>', '/assets/img/feedback/Shell-Deer-Park.jpg', 'Gerente de Turnaround', 'Feedback', 'pt-br', NULL, NULL),
(27, '22222222', '22222222', 'Shell Deer Park', '<p>Я думал, что все, что вы, ребята, делали, было круто, и я уже распространял рекомендации продолжать использовать вас, ребята, когда это возможно!</p>', '/assets/img/feedback/Shell-Deer-Park.jpg', 'Менеджер по обороту', 'Feedback', 'ru', NULL, NULL),
(28, '22222222', '22222222', 'Shell Deer Park', '<p>ฉันคิดว่าทุกสิ่งที่พวกคุณทำนั้นยอดเยี่ยมมากและได้เผยแพร่คำแนะนำเพื่อใช้กับพวกคุณต่อไปทุกเมื่อที่ทำได้!</p>', '/assets/img/feedback/Shell-Deer-Park.jpg', 'ผู้จัดการเทิร์นอะราวด์', 'Feedback', 'th', NULL, NULL),
(29, '33333333', '33333333', 'The Application Of Industrial Scale Ultrasonic Cleaning To Heat Exchangers', '<p>B. Kieser, R. Phillion, T. McCartney</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" alt=\"Tube Exchanger before and after cleaning.\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" /></a></p>\n            <p>The cleaning of fouled heat exchangers often presents a significant challenge to the maintenance and operation of chemical, petroleum and food processes.</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">Read more</span> &rarr;</a></p>', 'assets/img/tech-sonic-vessel-sm.jpg', NULL, 'Referred Journal Publications', 'en', NULL, NULL),
(30, '33333333', '33333333', '工业规模超声波清洗在热交换器中的应用', '<p>B. Kieser, R. Phillion, T. McCartney</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" alt=\"Tube Exchanger before and after cleaning.\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" /></a></p>\n            <p>积垢的热交换器的清洁通常对化学，石油和食品加工的维护和操作提出了重大挑战。</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">了解详情</span> &rarr;</a></p>', 'assets/img/tech-sonic-vessel-sm.jpg', NULL, 'Referred Journal Publications', 'cn', NULL, NULL),
(31, '33333333', '33333333', 'De toepassing van ultrasone reiniging op industriële schaal op warmtewisselaars', '<p>B. Kieser, R. Phillion, T. McCartney</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" alt=\"Tube Exchanger before and after cleaning.\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" /></a></p>\n            <p>Het reinigen van vervuilde warmtewisselaars vormt vaak een aanzienlijke uitdaging voor het onderhoud en de werking van chemische, petroleum- en voedselprocessen.</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">Lees meer</span> &rarr;</a></p>', 'assets/img/tech-sonic-vessel-sm.jpg', NULL, 'Referred Journal Publications', 'de', NULL, NULL),
(32, '33333333', '33333333', 'La aplicación de la limpieza ultrasónica a escala industrial a los intercambiadores de calor', '<p>B. Kieser, R. Phillion, T. McCartney</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" alt=\"Tube Exchanger before and after cleaning.\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" /></a></p>\n            <p>La limpieza de intercambiadores de calor sucios a menudo presenta un desafío significativo para el mantenimiento y operación de procesos químicos, petroleros y alimentarios.</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">Leer más</span> &rarr;</a></p>', 'assets/img/tech-sonic-vessel-sm.jpg', NULL, 'Referred Journal Publications', 'es-us', NULL, NULL),
(33, '33333333', '33333333', 'La aplicación de la limpieza ultrasónica a escala industrial a los intercambiadores de calor', '<p>B. Kieser, R. Phillion, T. McCartney</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" alt=\"Tube Exchanger before and after cleaning.\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" /></a></p>\n            <p>La limpieza de intercambiadores de calor sucios a menudo presenta un desafío significativo para el mantenimiento y operación de procesos químicos, petroleros y alimentarios.</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">Leer más</span> &rarr;</a></p>', 'assets/img/tech-sonic-vessel-sm.jpg', NULL, 'Referred Journal Publications', 'es', NULL, NULL),
(34, '33333333', '33333333', 'L\'application du nettoyage ultrasonique d\'échelle industrielle aux échangeurs de chaleur', '<p>B. Kieser, R. Phillion, T. McCartney</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" alt=\"Tube Exchanger before and after cleaning.\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" /></a></p>\n            <p>Le nettoyage des échangeurs de chaleur encrassés présente souvent un défi important pour l\'entretien et le fonctionnement des procédés chimiques, pétroliers et alimentaires.</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">En savoir plus</span> &rarr;</a></p>', 'assets/img/tech-sonic-vessel-sm.jpg', NULL, 'Referred Journal Publications', 'fr', NULL, NULL),
(35, '33333333', '33333333', 'हीट एक्सचेंजर्स को औद्योगिक स्केल अल्ट्रासोनिक सफाई का अनुप्रयोग', '<p>B. Kieser, R. Phillion, T. McCartney</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" alt=\"Tube Exchanger before and after cleaning.\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" /></a></p>\n            <p>फाउल्ड हीट एक्सचेंजर्स की सफाई अक्सर रासायनिक, पेट्रोलियम और खाद्य प्रक्रियाओं के रखरखाव और संचालन के लिए एक महत्वपूर्ण चुनौती प्रस्तुत करती है।</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">और पढ़ें</span> &rarr;</a></p>', 'assets/img/tech-sonic-vessel-sm.jpg', NULL, 'Referred Journal Publications', 'hi-in', NULL, NULL),
(36, '33333333', '33333333', '熱交換器への工業規模の超音波洗浄の応用', '<p>B. Kieser, R. Phillion, T. McCartney</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" alt=\"Tube Exchanger before and after cleaning.\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" /></a></p>\n            <p>汚れた熱交換器の洗浄は、化学、石油、食品プロセスの保守と運用に重大な課題をもたらすことがよくあります。</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">続きを読む</span> &rarr;</a></p>', 'assets/img/tech-sonic-vessel-sm.jpg', NULL, 'Referred Journal Publications', 'jp', NULL, NULL),
(37, '33333333', '33333333', 'Aplikasi Pembersihan Ultrasonik Skala Industri Untuk Penukar Panas', '<p>B. Kieser, R. Phillion, T. McCartney</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" alt=\"Tube Exchanger before and after cleaning.\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" /></a></p>\n            <p>Pembersihan penukar haba yang tercemar sering kali memberikan cabaran yang besar bagi penyelenggaraan dan pengendalian proses kimia, petroleum dan makanan.</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">Baca lebih lanjut/span> &rarr;</a></p>', 'assets/img/tech-sonic-vessel-sm.jpg', NULL, 'Referred Journal Publications', 'ml', NULL, NULL),
(38, '33333333', '33333333', 'La aplicación de la limpieza ultrasónica a escala industrial a los intercambiadores de calor', '<p>B. Kieser, R. Phillion, T. McCartney</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" alt=\"Tube Exchanger before and after cleaning.\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" /></a></p>\n            <p>La limpieza de intercambiadores de calor sucios a menudo presenta un desafío significativo para el mantenimiento y operación de procesos químicos, petroleros y alimentarios.</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">Leer más</span> &rarr;</a></p>', 'assets/img/tech-sonic-vessel-sm.jpg', NULL, 'Referred Journal Publications', 'mx', NULL, NULL),
(39, '33333333', '33333333', 'ਉਦਯੋਗਿਕ ਪੈਮਾਨੇ ਦੀ ਅਲਟਰਾਸੋਨਿਕ ਸਫਾਈ ਦੀ ਹੀਟ ਐਕਸਚੇਂਜਰਾਂ ਲਈ ਉਪਯੋਗਤਾ', '<p>B. Kieser, R. Phillion, T. McCartney</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" alt=\"Tube Exchanger before and after cleaning.\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" /></a></p>\n            <p>ਫਿledਲਡ ਹੀਟ ਐਕਸਚੇਂਜਰਾਂ ਦੀ ਸਫਾਈ ਅਕਸਰ ਰਸਾਇਣਕ, ਪੈਟਰੋਲੀਅਮ ਅਤੇ ਭੋਜਨ ਪ੍ਰਕਿਰਿਆਵਾਂ ਦੀ ਦੇਖਭਾਲ ਅਤੇ ਸੰਚਾਲਨ ਲਈ ਮਹੱਤਵਪੂਰਣ ਚੁਣੌਤੀ ਪੇਸ਼ ਕਰਦੀ ਹੈ.</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">ਹੋਰ ਪੜ੍ਹੋ</span> &rarr;</a></p>', 'assets/img/tech-sonic-vessel-sm.jpg', NULL, 'Referred Journal Publications', 'pa-pk', NULL, NULL),
(40, '33333333', '33333333', 'A aplicação de limpeza ultrassônica em escala industrial para trocadores de calor', '<p>B. Kieser, R. Phillion, T. McCartney</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" alt=\"Tube Exchanger before and after cleaning.\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" /></a></p>\n            <p>A limpeza de trocadores de calor sujos frequentemente apresenta um desafio significativo para a manutenção e operação de processos químicos, petrolíferos e alimentícios.</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">Leia mais</span> &rarr;</a></p>', 'assets/img/tech-sonic-vessel-sm.jpg', NULL, 'Referred Journal Publications', 'pt-br', NULL, NULL),
(41, '33333333', '33333333', 'Применение ультразвуковой очистки в промышленных масштабах для теплообменников', '<p>B. Kieser, R. Phillion, T. McCartney</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" alt=\"Tube Exchanger before and after cleaning.\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" /></a></p>\n            <p>Очистка загрязненных теплообменников часто представляет собой серьезную проблему для обслуживания и эксплуатации химических, нефтяных и пищевых производств.</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">Узнать больше</span> &rarr;</a></p>', 'assets/img/tech-sonic-vessel-sm.jpg', NULL, 'Referred Journal Publications', 'ru', NULL, NULL),
(42, '33333333', '33333333', 'การประยุกต์ใช้การทำความสะอาดอัลตราโซนิกในระดับอุตสาหกรรมกับเครื่องแลกเปลี่ยนความร้อน', '<p>B. Kieser, R. Phillion, T. McCartney</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" alt=\"Tube Exchanger before and after cleaning.\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/before-and-after-bundle-tubs-cleaned.jpg\" /></a></p>\n            <p>การทำความสะอาดเครื่องแลกเปลี่ยนความร้อนที่เปรอะเปื้อนมักเป็นความท้าทายที่สำคัญในการบำรุงรักษาและการดำเนินการของกระบวนการทางเคมีปิโตรเลียมและอาหาร</p>\n            <p><a href=\"http://www.heatexchanger-fouling.com/papers/papers2011/48_Kieser_F.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">อ่านเพิ่มเติม</span> &rarr;</a></p>', 'assets/img/tech-sonic-vessel-sm.jpg', NULL, 'Referred Journal Publications', 'th', NULL, NULL);

