(1, '11111111', 'Offsite Cleaning', 'assets/img/services/baytown-cleaning-facility.jpg', 'assets/img/services/baytown-cleaning-facility-sm.jpg', '<p>Getting results that are CLEANER, FASTER, SAFER and GREENER is easy! Our offsite facility in Baytown is ready to clean your fouled heat exchangers, filters, valves, rotating equipment, and many other parts.</p>\n            <ul>\n            <li>Most exchangers are cleaned in less than one day and often returned faster than you can clean it on your own wash pad.</li>\n            <li>We can clean almost any bundle to like new performance &ndash; and we guarantee it.\n            <h3><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">If we can&rsquo;t clean it, you don&rsquo;t pay!</span></h3>\n            </li>\n            <li>We can support both routine maintenance as well as turnarounds, with a cleaning capacity that will outpaced most wash pads.</li>\n            </ul>\n            <h4>&nbsp;</h4>\n            <p>Are you interested in:</p>\n            <ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n            <li><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" alt=\"Checkmark!\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" />&nbsp;Getting the risk of hydroblasting off of your site?</li>\n            <li><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" alt=\"Checkmark!\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" />&nbsp;Reducing your water consumption by 100%?</li>\n            <li><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" alt=\"Checkmark!\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" />&nbsp;Having exchangers that perform &ldquo;like new&rdquo;?</li>\n            </ul>\n            <p><a href=\"https://cleanasnew.com/contact\" aria-invalid=\"true\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">Call<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">us</span></span></a>&nbsp;today for our guaranteed, fixed price cleaner, faster, safer, greener services.</p>', 'assets/img/OffSiteMontage-min.gif\"', 'en', NULL, NULL),
(2, '11111111', '场外清洁', 'assets/img/services/baytown-cleaning-facility.jpg', 'assets/img/services/baytown-cleaning-facility-sm.jpg', '<p>获得更清洁，更快，更安全和更绿色的结果很容易！我们在Baytown的异地工厂可以随时清洁结垢的热交换器，过滤器，阀门，旋转设备以及许多其他零件。</p>\n            <ul>\n            <li>大多数交换器在不到一天的时间内进行清洁，而且返回的速度通常比您在自己的洗垫上清洁的速度快。</li>\n            <li>我们可以清理几乎所有捆绑包以使其具有新性能&ndash;我们保证。\n            <h3><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">如果我们无法清洁它，您就不用付款！</h3>\n            </li>\n            <li>我们可以为日常维护和周转提供支持，其清洁能力将超过大多数清洗垫。</li>\n            </ul>\n            <h4>&nbsp;</h4>\n            <p>您是否感兴趣：</p>\n            <ul>\n            <li><img src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" alt=\"&ldquo;检查标记！&quot;\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" /> 是否有发生喷水的风险？</li>\n            <li><img src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" alt=\"&ldquo;检查标记！&quot;\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" /> 可以将耗水量减少100％？</li>\n            <li><img src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" alt=\"&ldquo;检查标记！&quot;\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" /> 具有执行&ldquo;新\"功能的交换器吗？</li>\n            </ul>\n            <p><a href=\"https://cleanasnew.com/contact\" aria-invalid=\"true\">致电我们今天 </a>为我们提供的有保证，固定价格的清洁，更快，更安全，更环保的服务。</p>', 'assets/img/OffSiteMontage-min.gif\"', 'cn', NULL, NULL),
(3, '11111111', 'Offsite reiniging', 'assets/img/services/baytown-cleaning-facility.jpg', 'assets/img/services/baytown-cleaning-facility-sm.jpg', '<p>Resultaten behalen die SCHONER, SNELLER, VEILIGER en GROENER zijn, is eenvoudig! Onze externe faciliteit in Baytown staat klaar om uw vervuilde warmtewisselaars, filters, kleppen, roterende apparatuur en vele andere onderdelen te reinigen.</p>\n            <ul>\n            <li>De meeste wisselaars worden in minder dan een dag gereinigd en worden vaak sneller teruggestuurd dan dat u ze op uw eigen waskussen kunt reinigen.</li>\n            <li>We kunnen bijna elke bundel opschonen om van nieuwe prestaties te houden &amp; ndash; en we garanderen het.\n            <h3><span style=\"color: #3598db;\"><span style=\"color: #3598db;\">Als we het niet kunnen schoonmaken, betaal je niet!</span></h3>\n            </li>\n            <li>We kunnen zowel routineonderhoud als turnarounds ondersteunen, met een reinigingscapaciteit die de meeste waskussens overtreft.</li>\n            </ul>\n            <h4>&nbsp;</h4>\n            <p>Ben je ge&iuml;nteresseerd in:</p>\n            <ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n            <li><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" alt=\"Vinkje!\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" /> &amp; nbsp; Krijgt u het risico van hydroblast van uw site?</li>\n            <li><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" alt=\"Vinkje!\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" /> &amp; nbsp; Uw waterverbruik met 100% verminderen?</li>\n            <li><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" alt=\"Vinkje!\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" /> &amp; nbsp; Wisselaars hebben die &amp; ldquo; als nieuw presteren &amp; 